+Code the following app
+```
+Build a language learning quiz app to teach English speakers the language of Tagalog. Its title is “Learn Tagalog 🇵🇭” and it has simple cards that you flip and on one side it has emoji or English or Tagalog word, when you flip it it tells you what it is in Tagalog or English (opposite language to what was showing before you flipped it, if emoji image it must show Tagalog translation). Make it fun and colourful 
+```
+
+Generate an app logo and update the app metadata title and description.

